## Summary
This documentation describes the Twitter Ads cohort destination integration that enables syncing Amplitude user cohorts to Twitter Ads for audience creation, requiring OAuth authentication and supporting multiple user identifiers including Device ID, Email, Handle, X ID, and Phone Number with automatic SHA256 hashing.

